### A2A Calculator Agent - HTTP Requests
### Base URL - adjust port as needed
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7077
@a2aEndpoint = {{baseUrl}}/a2a

### Health Check
GET {{a2aEndpoint}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Agent Info/Welcome
GET {{a2aEndpoint}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Agent Card (Well-known endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/.well-known/agent-card.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Calculator - Addition (5 + 3)
POST {{a2aEndpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "calc-add-1",
  "method": "message/send",
  "params": {
    "id": "task-1",
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-1",
      "kind": "message",
      "role": "user",
      "contextId": "ctx-1",
      "parts": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "5 + 3"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}

